INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (314,1,'2011-02-15 06:24:31','2011-02-15 06:24:31','<h3>Donate to Sukrupa</h3>\r\n<a href=\"/donate/\">Donate now</a>, or sponsor a child to make SUKRUPA\'s goal a reality. Your donations keep us going. Support a child for Rs. 18,000/year, or under a dollar a day.\r\n\r\nFor more information, please <a href=\"http://sukrupa.localhost/contact/\">contact us</a>.\r\n<h3>Volunteer Opportunities</h3>\r\nA powerful and impactful way to touch the lives of our students, to adjust the course of a life, is to join the many volunteers who support the education of SUKRUPA kids by teaching. You can volunteer to teach in the following areas:\r\n<ul class=\"lined\">\r\n	<li>Pre-school</li>\r\n	<li>After school program</li>\r\n	<li>Basic computer lessons</li>\r\n	<li>Arts and crafts</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nYou can also join in by volunteering to:\r\n<ul class=\"lined\">\r\n	<li>Setup and design a newsletter</li>\r\n	<li>Sell products made at <a href=\"http://sukrupacreations.bigcartel.com\">SUKRUPA Creations</a></li>\r\n	<li>Create awareness about SUKRUPA at your workplace/networking group</li>\r\n	<li>Host a fundraiser party</li>\r\n	<li>Assist to help with events and special programs</li>\r\n	<li>Participate in “PROJECT CLASSROOM”- A school building project</li>\r\n	<li>Help raise funds</li>\r\n	<li>Pray for SUKRUPA and our donors, administrators, volunteers, and most importantly our children</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFor more information, please <a href=\"http://sukrupa.localhost/contact/\">contact us</a>.\r\n<h3>Observed Holidays</h3>\r\nPlease note that the following public holidays will be observed at Sukrupa. On most national holidays we mark the day with celebrations at the school. However if you plan to visit or volunteer during these days, be sure to call us to confirm in advance.\r\n\r\nIn the summer, the students are on vacation between the 2nd and 27th of May 2011. Additionally, you can contact us to receive the student exam schedule to plan your visit be