11</td>\r\n<td>Good Friday</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>May 17th, 2011</td>\r\n<td>Buddha Purnima</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>August 13th, 2011</td>\r\n<td>Raksha Bandhan</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>August 15th, 2011</td>\r\n<td>Independence Day</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>August 30th, 2011</td>\r\n<td>End of Ramadan</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>October 2nd, 2011</td>\r\n<td>Gandhi Jayanthi</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>October 6th, 2011</td>\r\n<td>Dussehra</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>October 26th, 2011</td>\r\n<td>Diwali</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>November 6th, 2011</td>\r\n<td>Bakrid</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>November 10th, 2011</td>\r\n<td>Guru Nanak’s Birthday</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>December 5th, 2011</td>\r\n<td>Muharram</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>December 25th 2011</td>\r\n<td>Christmas Day</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','Supporting Sukrupa','<a href=\"http://sukrupa.localhost/donate/\">Donating now is the best way to help us out.</a> Your donations of all sizes keep us going. An 18,000 Rs (about $396 USD) donation supports a child at SUKRUPA for one year. If you want to sponsor a child with particular needs or have any questions, please contact us.','inherit','open','open','','17-revision-15','','','2011-02-15 12:42:49','2011-02-15 12:42:49','',17,'http://sukrupa.localhost/uncategorized/17-revision-15/',0,'revision','',0);
